Our App is SAFE and we NEVER collect data from you!
We are a registered company in Seoul, Korea, dedicating ourselves to making safe apps for all ages. We are parents ourselves and we make apps as if they were for our own kids. Please rest assured that Video Call Santa is 100% safe.
Video calls are not real calls
All our video call episodes are pre-recorded. Everything is pre-recorded, and no one is looking at or talking to your children.
We cannot see you or spy on you
The request for permission to access your camera and microphone is only so your children can appear on the chat screen and to allow your videos to be recorded.
Recordings are only for you to save or share
Only you have access to your conversation recordings. You can turn off the recording function in the Settings if you prefer.
We never have access to your information such as your name or your phone number
None of your contact information is given out. We do not collect any data from you at any time.
We never send out any marketing calls or texts
If you are getting any suspicious calls or texts, they are not from us. We do not use any telemarketing or text marketing whatsoever.
